column8: TRAFFIC LIGHT BLOWN INTO STREET ON PLEASANTBURG DR WIND ESTIMATED GREATER THAN 50 MPH (GSP)
TREE DOWN AT SHRINE CLUB RD AND HWY 28 WITH A POWER POLE DOWN AT HAGLER STREET EXT. (GSP)
SEVERAL TREES AND WIRES WERE KNOCKED DOWN IN FORKS TOWNSHIP AND PALMER TOWNSHIP. REPORT WAS RELAYED BY PEMA AND LOCAL MEDIA. (PHI)
